AFRICAN DANCE, a workshop taught by Sara Wendt with traditional drum rhythms of Africa, for children 8 and up, $10 a person. At Elisabeth Irwin High School, 40 Charlton Street, between Avenue of the Americas and Varick Street, Manhattan. Sunday at 1:30 P.M. Reservations: (212) 477-5316.

